params.1319:
Callisto is an enormous bear empowered by the corruption of the Wilderness. He resides south of the Demonic Ruins in the Wilderness.

Attack Styles - Melee, Special
Immunities - Poison, Venom, Magic
Slayer categories - Bear
params.1320:
